  "title": "Pigeonpea collection in Luzon, Philippines",
  "abstract": "Pigeonpea is not one of the major field crops of the Philippines. The cultivation is limited to small gardens around the house and field bunds. Most of the produce is consumed by the growers and hence seldom found in the market...",
